e\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ΚαλλικράτεοςΚαλικράτεος Μεννάδος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ΚαλλικράτεοςΚαλικράτεος\">Καλικράτεος\u003C/span>  \u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μεννάδος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronymic\" data-text=\"Μεννάδος\">Μεννάδος\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ε̄̓μί \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 reg., orig. ΚΑΛΙΚΡΑΤΕΟΣΚαλικράτεος\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>ΤΑΣ\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"ΚαλλικράτεοςΚαλικράτεος Μεννάδος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"ΚαλλικράτεοςΚαλικράτεος\">ΚΑΛΙΚΡΑΤΕΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Μεννάδος\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronymic\" data-text=\"Μεννάδος\">ΜΕΝΝΑΔΟΣ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>Ε̄ΜΙ\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">l.1 reg., orig. ΚΑΛΙΚΡΑΤΕΟΣΚαλικράτεος\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020448_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020448_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic020448.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic020448-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text after Arena 1989 (IGASM I)\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Tusa: Καλικράτεος Μένναρός ε̄̓μι.\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Villa: Μενναδο͂ς.\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>I am (the krater) of Mennados (son) of Kallikratos.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7122-2511\">Valentina Mignosa\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Sono (il cratere) di Mennados (figlio) di Kallikratos.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The first mu (initial of the name Μεννάδος) seems to have a very different ductus from the second one (in ε̄̓μί): the difference could be explained, according to Arena, by assuming an intervention by the writer who would have written a pi at first and then amended it to mu. The name Μεννάδος is not elsewhere attested.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Tusa 1971 27, pl. 6d \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001534\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001534\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Villa 1979 64ff., fig. 1, pl. 12, figs. 1-2 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001461\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001461\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Arena 1989 74, fig. 12 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000638\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cl